title: Mohamed Antar - 2009 - Oriental Breeze
description: Mohammed Antar is a Ney player, and founder and conductor of Ensemble Munajah, 2003. He started his musical educations at the age of four and was exposed to Ney in 1993. He studied and mastered its different blowing and playing styles. He participated in various national and international musical events as a soloist or with different musical groups. He also participated in recordings by Asil and Ishq ensembles.
